then this is the Batman for you.Best Dark Real GOTHAM BATMAN. A MUST SEE!!!If you were expecting The Dark Knight walking intothis movie, then you will for sure be dissapointed. Butif you are expecting just absolute beautiful cinema;then this is the Batman for you.Mathew Reeves is a genius. A genius for following theComics portrayal of The Batman. For the first 10 minof the movie I got a little nervous because it wasn'tthe Batman that I was used to. But after a little bit ofseeing the most Accurate Bruce Wayne and mostaccurate Batman combo, I was surely surely satisfied.Overall, the writing in this movie and cinematographyis just perfect. Perfect perfect perfect. And a hugethanks to Michael Giachino for being the bestcomposer of all time next to James Newton Howardand Hans Zimmer.As for the acting. There could not. And I repeat couldnot have been a better cast. Paul Dani made themovie alone with his preference on the Rider. Justgenius. And if I didn't know before the movie thatColin Ferral was the penguin, I would have neverguessed it. As for Robert Pattinson; bravo my friend.You played the absolute best version of The Batmanthat anyone could ask for. Where as with the otherBatman's, they were seen as two characters (Batmanand Bruce Wayne), your version matched the Comicsof the right balance of Billionaire Playboy and theright balance of dark rich vigilante. And Zoe's actingcan go without saying as the perfect cat woman too.Hot, sexy, straight to the chase, hurt, broken, andFlexible.The movie deserves an 8.6 rating but I’m giving it a nine to boost the rating.
